                  <td valign="bottom"><h2><a href="extraction-arms.html">Extraction arms ERGO</a></h2>
                    <p>Extraction arms ERGO are designed to remove smoke, dust and gases directly at emission source before the contamination has spread into the                      workshop area and could   be inhaled. Properly adjusted frictional articulations of ERGO arm with the cooperation of gas springs make maneuvering very easy.</p>
