                  <td valign="bottom"><h2><a href="filtering-units.html">Air filtering units</a></h2>
                    <p>Filtering units are designed to remove and filter air with fumes and airborne particles during welding, grinding, polishing or any other                      technological operations which create   pollution. Units are equipped with filter regeneration system.</p>
                    <p class="more"><a href="filtering-units.html">More information</a></p></td>
